name: FROSTLINE 002: Techno and Tech-House Rave
description:
Join us for the first rave of 2026!

Expect driving techno, rolling tech-house, low lights, and a room built for the dancefloor. No countdown, no champagne. Just music, movement, and cold energy.

The night opens with Soul Sista, setting the tone before transitioning into Frostline's signature techno and tech-house sets from JAEN, Lito, SHERM, and Eazy Ej.
